description: The Joker is back in Arkham Asylum and Harley Quinn breaks back in with him - but is she there to stand by him or destroy him? Either way, Poison Ivy and Catwoman must put aside their tumultuous past to help their wayward friend. Guest-starring Clayface and Batman!
name: Vol. 4

description:
Tells of Kaisa Lekas decision to have her legs amputated, and replaced with prosthetics. And also of the life after that.

A black and white comic.

Based on a true story.
name: I am not these feet.

The world is a lonely place when you're a man without a home --- just ask Kev Hawkins. After murdering his boss in a nasty government scheme, he's banished from the United Kingdom under pain of death. What does the world hold for a man with little life experience or training beyond wetworks and assassinations? Then again, with the past about to catch up with Kev in the most violent and terrifying way possible, what the world hods for him may be besides the point...

This best-selling series re-teams the internationally renowned creators Garth Ennis (PREACHER) and Carlos Ezquerra (JUDGE DREDD) for the final chapter in the saga of Kev Hawkins.
